<h2 id="about">ABOUT US</h2>
<p class="p1">Gopalan Enterprises, inspired by life - built on trust - was founded in 1984 by its Chairman, Architect C. Gopalan, and being successfully run along with his sons Architect C. Pramod and Architect C. Prabhakar with the objective of developing and constructing value added residential and commercial spaces in Bangalore.</p>
</br>
<p class="p1">Gopalan believes in deriving real value for money, whether it is residential or retail destination. The ultra-modern glass structure has a retail space of over two lakh square feet spread over multiple floors. Gopalan Malls house 2 Screens Multiplex, Fine Dining area, a Food Court with Entertainment Zone,Children Play Area, Hypermarket and Retail Brands show rooms.<p>
</br>
<p class="p1">Malls :
 <ol>
	<li>ARCADE MALL</li>
	<li>SIGNATURE MALL</li>
	<li>INNOVATION MALL</li>
 </ol>
</p>
</br>

